short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Follow subscribers in YouTube quickly and reliably, quick access to subscribers in YouTube

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The YouTube subscription itself is an application that allows you to quickly and conveniently keep track of the latest updates to your subscriptions without logging into the YouTube page. You just need to add the address of your channel once and for the last how many hours the published videos items you want to see. The application will only evolve and will add more and more new features just for your convenience.
